Data will be &quot;compiled&quot; into binary form by some &quot;commit/version&quot; tool and  &quot;rolled back&quot; back to text form or queried by another tools.

To clarify more, let's see some usage examples in Unix shell:

sh&gt; $EDITOR file.txt
File saved.

